result.adr_address: 1-41, 18 Harcourt Rd, Admiralty, Hong Kong
result.name: McDonald's

reviews.text: There is a huge selection of items here. You can build your own burger which I have never seen before. The store is mostly crowded but clean and has a friendly atmosphere
Huge selection of items here. Busy store..Be prepared for a wait but there are a lot of customers at this location. Food is good and served fresh.
One of the best gourmet burgers I’ve ever had at a McDonald’s. Everything was perfect and juicy inside the burger and their chocopie dessert is one of the greatest creations at McDonald’s ever.
I got a nice ice cream cone for a dessert. I'm loving it. The price is good too. This one, I paid $13 Hong Kong $ which is less than $2 USD.

The food comes out fast, but there is nothing special about it. The coffee foam smells like cheese so watch out for that. It's way better than McDonald's in the US, but not as good as other restaurants in Hong Kong

result.adr_address: 1-41, 18 Harcourt Rd, Admiralty, 香港
result.name: 麥當勞

reviews.text: 奶茶不合意了☕😩
今天在金鐘麥當勞遺下個人物品，我快速致電佢地幫忙揾，佢地就極快速揾返兼打俾我，速度之高真係于欲無言。。。多謝哂蔡小姐👍😊如果你係香港政府就好lu😅
There is a huge selection of items here. You can build your own burger which I have never seen before. The store is mostly crowded but clean and has a friendly atmosphere
前兩日經過軒尼詩道的麥當奴食咗個三点三價錢都是$16元就有迷你包加ㄧ杯熱飲都算ok啦

好耐冇悠悠閒咁歎麥記 clay
-
麥當勞真係由細食到大，食左咁多十年對佢既鍾愛情度冇點變。 一黎分店多，總有一間你左右，二黎味道如一，咁多十年都保持到standard 味道。
上星期五朋友約我去海洋公園，佢話有生日優惠🤪 雖然成32度高溫真係唔多想郁，但佢興致勃勃叫到點都要陪下既。冇理由成日掛住拍拖冇哂朋友。
一早約定先去金鐘麥記食過靚早餐先，黎過珍寶餐！份量多夠哂飽，質素唔錯，雖然人流極多，但不馬虎，食物夠熱！ 最鍾意佢既炒蛋，幾滑幾香，屋企無論點整都整唔到😆。仲有兩大塊軟熟熱香餅，搽上牛油及淋上楓糖漿，滋味無比！ 
當然仲有香脆薯餅，油澀得夠乾不膩。 由細到大都咁鍾意食！同埋一定要放最後食！慢慢歎
再整杯熱豆漿！ 佢既豆香好重，仲要少甜，唔錯！
